{"word":"Edom","slug":"edom","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Edom</b> <a href=\"#/H123\">H123</a> <br/> Signifies red.<br/> 1. A name of Esau, possibly on account of his being covered with red hair<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=25'>Gen 25:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=30'>Gen 25:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=1'>Gen 36:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=8'>Gen 36:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=19'>Gen 36:19</a><br/> 2. A name of the land occupied by the descendants of Esau<br/> - Extended from the Elanitic Gulf to the Red Sea, and was called Idumea<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=32&verse=3'>Gen 32:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=17'>Gen 36:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=21'>Gen 36:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=40&verse=11'>Jer 40:11</a> <br/> - Noted for its wise men<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=31&chapter=1&verse=8'>Oba 1:8</a> <br/> - Sins of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=31&chapter=1&verse=14'>Oba 1:14</a> <br/> - Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=25&verse=23'>Jer 25:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=27&verse=11'>Jer 27:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=11&verse=41'>Dan 11:41</a><br/><a href='S:Edomites'>Edomites</a> <br/> - Figurative of the foes of Zion<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=63&verse=1'>Isa 63:1</a> <br/> - Wilderness of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=3&verse=8'>2Ki 3:8</a> "}]}